  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个风险响应流程图，核心是从Redis缓存出发，经过Etcd集群做决策判断，然后分发到不同的基础设施组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是Infra_RedisCache，然后连到Infra_EtcdCluster做分支判断。这个Etcd节点是菱形判断框还是普通节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Etcd这里要做决策，用菱形。它根据风险等级分出三条路径：高风险走WorkerNode，中高风险回到Etcd自身做进一步处理，中低风险走IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把结构搭出来：A是Redis缓存矩形，B是Etcd菱形判断，然后B分出三条带标签的边到C、D、E。标签分别是\"高\"、\"中高\"、\"中/低\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，D节点我需要再确认一下。中高风险的响应是触发Etcd集群的自我修复流程，所以D应该还是Infra_EtcdCluster，但代表的是一个内部协调动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "了解，那C、D、E三个下游节点分别是：C-WorkerNode处理高风险，D-EtcdCluster自身处理中高风险，E-IngressController处理中低风险。之后它们怎么汇聚？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "三条路径最后都要回到Redis缓存做状态更新，我加一个F节点作为统一的状态汇聚点，然后再流转到G节点做最终的WorkerNode执行确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加F节点，C、D、E都指向F。不过这里有个问题：F我标注为Infra_RedisCache，但前面A已经是Redis了，这样会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "你说得对，A和F都是RedisCache，但在流程里A是触发源，F是响应后的状态回写，实际上是同一个组件的不同阶段。Mermaid里可以复用同一个标识，这样连线更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，那F也用Infra_RedisCache。然后F到G是最后一步，G是Infra_WorkerNode做执行确认。整个流程闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再检查一下边的关系：B到C是高风险，B到D是中高风险，B到E是中低风险。C、D、E到F是并行汇聚，F到G是最终执行。有没有遗漏？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构都齐了。我调整一下布局让菱形B居中，三条分支线从上往下排布，最后汇聚到F再指向G。视觉上应该很清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来没问题。这个流程覆盖了从风险检测、分级响应到状态回写的完整闭环。WorkerNode既作为高风险的处理节点，也作为最终执行确认点，逻辑上是自洽的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我注意到B到D的边标签是\"中高\"，但D也是Infra_EtcdCluster，和B同名。要不要在标签上写得更明确一些，比如\"触发协调\"？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持\"中高\"就行，这是风险等级的标准命名。上下文里从菱形B出发，读者能理解这是Etcd的自我协调流程。标签简洁更重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，最终确认：7个节点，A-B-C-D-E-F-G，其中B是菱形判断，A/F是Redis，B/D是Etcd，C/E/G涉及WorkerNode和IngressController。所有连线都已标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，这个风险响应流程图可以定稿了。从Infra_RedisCache触发，经Infra_EtcdCluster分级，最终回到缓存并确认执行，逻辑完整。",
